cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.IR 

The paper uses deep recurrent neural network with Long Short-Term Memory units for time-series data analysis and prediction. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also discusses the use of encoder-decoder model, which is a common technique in natural language processing, covered by cs.NE. The paper also deals with the analysis of data and the evaluation of prediction accuracy, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and statistical learning (cs.SI).
